column5: ive been trying to find a frabill rainsuit. F2 surge suit is what im looking for.  I've been to BPS, and Sail..with no luck.   I could purchase online, but id like to try on first.
Canadian Tire is where I bought mine.
LeBarons has them. Just bought a pair of bibs the other day. $130 for the bibs, jacket is the same price.
